@jankatins, this may feel a bit hacky, but you can actually restore the default values like this:

```python
class MyClass(HasTraits):
    i = Int()
    d = Dict()

mc = MyClass()
mc.i = 2
mc.d = {"a": 1}
# no we clear trait values
