It looks like you are running the example from: http://docs.graphene-python.org/projects/django/en/latest/tutorial-plain/#testing-our-graphql-schema

But that github repository is from the example using Relay, so your query should be:
```
query {
  allIngredients {
    edges {
      node {
        id,
        name
      }
    }
  }
}
```
